      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(msteams): escape markup in mention display names",
        "body": "## Problem\n`parseMentions` interpolates the mention display name directly into `<at>${name}</at>` without escaping `&`/`<`/`>`. A name containing those characters breaks the Teams activity markup and desyncs `entity.text` from the rendered `<at>` tag.\n\n## Fix\nEscape `&`/`<`/`>` and use the same escaped name for both the tag text and `entity.text` so the Teams text/entity contract holds.\n\n## Proof\nAdded a regression in `extensions/msteams/src/mentions.test.ts` — fails before, passes after. Pure function unit test.\n",
